| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0356 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b2dfb57d-0078-5b6f-8541-f9341c2e8fd5"
